clue: To post a message originally posted by someone else on the service now known as X

response: retweet

clue: This word for a now-ubiquitous form of entertainment program comes in part from an Apple product

response: a podcast

clue: What used to be a "buddy movie" depicting an affectionate relationship between 2 guys is now this blended word

response: a bromance

clue: You hit this annoying thing when a website demands a fee to read content kept "behind" it

response: a paywall

clue: From the French, it's the sport of running, jumping & climbing around & over urban obstacles

response: parkour

